# CV Collector Backend Rules

## Tech Stack
- Runtime: Node.js + Express
- Database: SQLite
- Language: JavaScript
- OCR: Tesseract.js

## Project Structure
- src/api/ - API routes
- src/services/ - Business logic
- src/skills/ - Custom skills
- uploads/ - File storage

## Naming Conventions
- Files: kebab-case (talent.service.js)
- Functions: camelCase (getTalentById)
- Routes: kebab-case (/api/talents)

## Best Practices
- Validasi input di controller
- Error handling dengan try-catch
- Response format konsisten: { success, data, error }

## Code Style
- Gunakan async/await (bukan .then())
- Destructuring untuk clean code
- Arrow functions untuk callbacks